Onece upon a time there lived a monkey on a mango tree. The tree was located at a riverbank. Crocodiles inhabited the river.
The monkey became friend with a crocodile.

By the time they bacame best friends. the monkey would give sweet ripen mangoes to the crocodile whenever he came to
meet him.One day the crocodile took some mangoes to his wife. His wife was very delighted to eat the sweet mangoes.
But then a cunning thought came to his wife's mind. She thought that what fun would it be to eat the monkey"s heart.
